                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Structure",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The simplicity of the table structure contributes to efficient data access and minimal overhead in terms of storage and maintenance."
